{"tid":2355225,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立場： 黑警指議助不能直播搜證過程 否則違反法庭禁令","createTime":"2021-01-06T04:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T04:40:49.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"bcbd5e94c1b8bcaf3c4c1cca35ef8bebcac69df9","tid":2355225,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:11:42.000Z","msg":"【警帶王百羽到議辦搜查　警告助理勿直播】<br />\n<br />\n不斷更新報道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/38i2EeP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F38i2EeP&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImXIsb0SIwbGp5IKHDv9YBGc%3D&h=24a38bc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/38i2EeP</a><br />\n<br />\n警方周三（6 日）早上大規模拘捕民主派人士，指控他們籌備和參與民主派 35+ 立法會初選，涉嫌違反《港區國安法》。目前逾 50 人被捕，包括曾與初選的元朗區議員王百羽。<br />\n<br />\n警員較早前進入王百羽的議員辦公室，並帶王入議辦搜證。其議員助理表示，當時被警員帶到外面登記資料後，並在外等待，但議助用手機進行直播不久，有 4 名警員走出來指他拍攝到警員樣貌，涉嫌違反禁制令，喝令他立即停止直播。議助反問是違反那條禁制令條例時，該警員回答，「我而家冇喺身」、「我而家就係話你違反咗法庭禁制令。」<br />\n<br />\n警員亦核對在場記者的資料。<br />\n<br />\n王百羽其後被帶上私家車後座離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://fb.watch/2QYwuDBfaY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.watch%2F2QYwuDBfaY%2F&d=dNeHxx%2FttK3%2FgpwSwFVImXIsb0SIwbGp5IKHDv9YBGc%3D&h=8523d8e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.watch/2QYwuDBfaY/</a>"},{"pid":"74c6cbc60a56c71ee121785bfacf51afd27539f9","tid":2355225,"uid":304431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:11:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84e3c7554c8d77ef27dfa0f7bedc477873a2b852","tid":2355225,"uid":53498,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:13:01.000Z","msg":"口講就係法律<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb6e3adad5c97de0bcfaaa81e97d769b99ac088","tid":2355225,"uid":214502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10f202887216624a26c0fd4c3065